## Why this structure (traceability)

| IA Section | Traces back to |
|---|---|
| Day 1 checklist + progress tracker | H1 — overwhelming Day 1, no visibility of next step |
| Key Documents (single source) | H2 — all 6 participants split search across 3+ systems |
| Help and Support (contacts + AI) | H3 — didn't know who to ask; wanted source-cited, transparent AI |
| Week 1 role-specific tasks | H4 — training felt generic, disconnected from actual role |

## Mapped to the journey map stages
- **Pre-arrival / Day 1** → Home, Day 1 section
- **First week** → Week 1 section, Key Documents
- **First month** → Progress Overview, ongoing Help and Support
